To begin with,you need to install those tools below:
	automake 1.11 or higher
	autoconf 2.63 or higher
	gcc 4.4.0 or higher
	make 3.81 or higher

Step 1:
	Get libcda from http://libcda.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/libcda

		svn checkout http://libcda.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/libcda
		cd libcda/
		./configure
		make
		make install

Step 2:
	Get libxmlo from http://libxmo.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/libxmlo

		svn checkout http://libxmo.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/libxmlo
		cd libxmlo/
		./configure
		make
		make install

Step 3:
	Get sparrows from http://sparrows.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/sparrows

		svn checkout http://sparrows.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/sparrows
		cd sparrows/
		./configure
		make
		cd mods/
		./build

